episodes.title: Claire Ashman | #062 The freedom of choice
episodes.description:
Never before have I met someone who wants to live life to the full like Claire Ashman.

It all makes sense when you discover that she is a cult survivor, of not one but two cults in Australia. Her attitude is one of life being an experiment and she is not willing to waste any opportunity. 

Discussing her resilience and tenacity in a world she knew nothing about is uplifting. It will make you rethink the freedom you have and the power of your choice.

Inspire yourself with these essential insights from Claire Ashman
